Append a Substrait Project Relation

substrait_filter.Rd

Append a Substrait Project Relation

Usage

substrait_filter(.compiler, ...)

Arguments

.compiler

A substrait_compiler() or object that can be coerced to one

...

Filter expressions

Value

A modified .compiler

Examples

substrait_filter(
  duckdb_substrait_compiler(data.frame(a = 1, b = "one")),
  a > 0
)
